QuestData.Title: Bring Me A Shrubbery!
QuestData.Description: My people use sanguine hibiscus for a number of purposes.$B$BIt grows naturally only in the Underbog, and many of the bog's denizens have taken a liking to it.$B$BIf you could bring me some, I would be very grateful.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 5 Sanguine Hibiscus and return them to T'shu in the Underbog.
QuestData.CompletionText: Were you able to gather any hibiscus?
QuestData.RewardText: These will do nicely, but we can always use more. Perhaps you will find yourself in the Underbog again soon?
